text.tspan: draggr is a drag-and-drop personal scheduling tool app built in Angular.
Unlike other scheduling tools, the tasks on your calendar are completely mal
leable: resizable, moveable, with tasks moving themselves automagically when
needed. Rescheduling one task doesnt mean rescheduling the whole day!
I focused on creating a smooth UI that, with further development, will lend
itself to gamification of users productivity.
Currently, I consider it in an early-alpha stage. Ive made it open-source,
and plan on developing a whole array of features in the future. Very much
aiming towards something I would find useful for daily use myself.
